title: Rick.Stein.Tastes.the.Blues.x264-SM
description:
Rick.Stein.Tastes.the.Blues.x264-SM

 Ever since the early 1960s, Rick Stein has been in love
with the blues and years later he is fascinated by the dishes
ingrained in its lyrics - fried chicken and turnip greens, 
catfish and black-eyed peas, and the rest. In this film, 
Rick pays homage to the musicians who created this 
music and to the great dishes of the Mississippi Delta
that go hand in hand with the blues.
